127.net/B8-yoWYHl2eINx-wEBdwKg==/8796093025516466500 />\n<h3>妙手大仙医</h3>\n<p>金佛</p>\n<p>陈万里获得仙人传承，一朝觉醒，便如龙飞九天。\n一手握惊世医术，活死人肉白骨，达官显贵尽低头！一手持杀人利剑，斩破虚空，举世强者亦折服！\n从此红颜相伴，兄弟相随，纵情都市……</p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span>连载</span>\n  \n  <span>科幻</span>\n  <span>215.79万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                    </a>\n              \t</li>\n                \n              \t\n                <li class=\"m-book-single f-cb\">\n                    <a href=/reader/book/bd_750bc41317254264ad384f5234c5bb78_4 data-log=\"wa3-2:category=man,eventId=click,bookId=bd_750bc41317254264ad384f5234c5bb78_4\" title=\"都市沉浮\">\n                      \n<img src=https://easyreadfs.nosdn.127.net/U2eN0SsHzCGzzFScKNZusA==/8796093024875330232 />\n<h3>都市沉浮</h3>\n<p>易克1</p>\n<p>老板突然出事，乔梁惨遭重挫，更可怕的是他落入了一个精心布置的圈套……</p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span>连载</span>\n  \n  <span>都市</span>\n  <span>990.60万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                    </a>\n              \t</li>\n                \n              \t\n                <li class=\"m-book-single f-cb\">\n                    <a href=/reader/book/bd911e6618674cdb98bfea06b975abc4_4 data-log=\"wa3-2:category=man,eventId=click,bookId=bd911e6618674cdb98bfea06b975abc4_4\" title=\"官场：从离婚后扶摇直上\">\n                      \n<img src=https://easyreadfs.nosdn.127.net/sacmfcD8wCEBAn1SwzlM1w==/8796093025403494913 />\n<h3>官场：从离婚后扶摇直上</h3>\n<p>天涯行者</p>\n<p>普普通通的机关科员姜云山刚被亿万富豪前妻嫌弃离了婚，转身就娶了背景惊人，强势霸道的女领导。　　蹉跎五年的仕途之路就此骤然爆发生机，一路青云直上，扶摇万里。　　前妻说：“他的才华不应该浪费在仕途之上…”　　现任说：“仕途才是他真正应该纵横的疆场…”　　前妻与现任，权势与财富，交织纠缠着，成就了姜云山不一样的官场人生。</p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span>完结</span>\n  \n  <span>都市</span>\n  <span>302.78万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                    </a>\n              \t</li>\n                \n            </ul>\n        </section>\n        <section class=\"m-swiper-box\">\n            <div class=\"swiper-container\">\n                <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n                \n                \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n  \t\t\n        <section class=\"m-list-box\">\n            <h3 class=\"f-cb\">\n                <span class=\"gradient\">都市爽文</span>\n                <a href=\"/column/3001.do\" class=\"more\" data-log=\"wa5-0:category=man,eventId=click\">更多</a>\n            </h3>\n            \n            \n             <li class=\"m-book-single f-cb\">\n                <a href=/reader/book/ts_27659ae8de6e4adab68a44677b1bfb68_4  data-log=\"wa5-2:category=man,eventId=click,bookId=ts_27659ae8de6e4adab68a44677b1bfb68_4\" title=\"梦里千年修仙，醒来后我无敌\">\n                  \n<img src=https://easyreadfs.nosdn.127.net/TzxqKAvQGhIJhMlcIPHGKA==/8796093025475253671 />\n<h3>梦里千年修仙，醒来后我无敌</h3>\n<p>逍遥大篷车</p>\n<p>三年植物人，梦里修仙已千年！林白醒来发现一切成真，梦里的九大圣女老婆，居然也都重生了！</p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span>连载</span>\n  \n  <span>都市</span>\n  <span>224.63万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                </a>\n          \t</li>\n            \n            \n             <li class=\"m-book-single f-cb\">\n                <a href=/reader/book/b12416cbe02344128f5e3b27319aec60_4  data-log=\"wa5-2:category=man,eventId=click,bookId=b12416cbe02344128f5e3b27319aec60_4\" title=\"官道风云\">\n                  \n<img src=https://easyreadfs.nosdn.127.net/xuuqiNftJChZSaQrpn-qBw==/8796093025408209058 />\n<h3>官道风云</h3>\n<p>风和暖阳</p>\n<p>天地有正道，人间有正气。法官萧明不畏强权，不图金钱，秉持初心，手握法槌，面对各种势力，斗智斗勇，翻手为云，覆手为雨，一路升迁，一路红颜，一路行走在为老百姓主持公平正义的道路上……</p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span>连载</span>\n  \n  <span>都市</span>\n  <span>15.41万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                </a>\n          \t</li>\n            \n            \n             <li class=\"m-book-single f-cb\">\n                <a href=/reader/book/3077fda591e544669caa8154299ddb65_4  data-log=\"wa5-2:category=man,eventId=click,bookId=3077fda591e544669caa8154299ddb65_4\" title=\"高考落榜，我手搓机甲震惊全球！\">\n                  \n<img src=https://easyreadfs.nosdn.127.net/nbVE14Z-YFbbEDZBjSe8ZQ==/8796093025478821674 />\n<h3>高考落榜，我手搓机甲震惊全球！</h3>\n<p>闹闹拉粑从不埋</p>\n<p>　　龙历2540年6月8日，随着华国最后一道防线被破。　　全球正式陷入死亡倒计时！　　自然灾害、异兽浪潮、雷电风暴纷至沓来。　　时任华国研究院的负责人顾龙洲看着满城风雨，却无能为力。　　人类，就此灭绝！　　……　　2530年6月8日，顾龙洲突然在课桌上惊醒。　　再度睁开眼时，他竟发现自己已然重生。　　执行《御天计划》、修筑钢铁长城、手搓太平洋机甲……　　异兽浪潮？雷电风暴？自然灾害？　　皆被我一一拦下！　　我顾龙洲这一世，要用一己之力拯救华国苍生！</p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span>完结</span>\n  \n  <span>都市</span>\n  <span>10.23万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                </a>\n          \t</li>\n            \n        </section>\n        <section class=\"m-list-box\">\n            <h3 class=\"f-cb\">\n                <span class=\"gradient\">大家都在看</span>\n                <a href=\"/column/2002.do\" class=\"more\" data-log=\"wa6-0:category=man,eventId=click\">更多</a>\n            </h3>\n            \n          \t\n            <div class=\"m-book-single f-cb\">\n                <a href=/reader/book/undefined data-log=\"wa6-2:category=man,eventId=click,bookId=ts_e9ca1483e61d44e9ac76007b9082e383_4\" title=\"\">\n                  \n<img src= />\n<h3></h3>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span></span>\n  <span>NaN万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                </a>\n            </div>\n            \n          \t\n            <div class=\"m-book-single f-cb\">\n                <a href=/reader/book/ba16df96cb3c485ea6b054dbc255e62c_4 data-log=\"wa6-2:category=man,eventId=click,bookId=ba16df96cb3c485ea6b054dbc255e62c_4\" title=\"凌云官途\">\n                  \n<img src=https://easyreadfs.nosdn.127.net/U_QTZQ67csvn5oa2AxmwFw==/8796093025443699872 />\n<h3>凌云官途</h3>\n<p>大江安澜</p>\n<p>他以为她要的是岁月静好、你侬我侬，为了娶她与家族决裂。直到她甩出一张离婚协议和亲子鉴定书，才知道一切都是假的。她要的，自始至终都是无上的权力！既如此，那就离婚吧！什么情比金坚，什么韬光养晦，都去他的！他要踏上青云之巅，碾碎这些蝇营狗苟，笑拥红颜，朗朗清平！（纯属虚构，不必较真，如有雷同，纯属巧合。）</p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span>连载</span>\n  \n  <span>都市</span>\n  <span>93.25万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                </a>\n            </div>\n            \n          \t\n            <div class=\"m-book-single f-cb\">\n                <a href=/reader/book/ts_d0396088a92a4f4e81951656d6577bfe_4 data-log=\"wa6-2:category=man,eventId=click,bookId=ts_d0396088a92a4f4e81951656d6577bfe_4\" title=\"我和离婚主妇\">\n                  \n<img src=https://easyreadfs.nosdn.127.net/zM91aqpCZ9JtVRyrVQsWeQ==/8796093025344141081 />\n<h3>我和离婚主妇</h3>\n<p>东门小官人</p>\n<p>穿着情趣内衣被赶出家门的已婚主妇，半夜在门口求收留</p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span>完结</span>\n  \n  <span>都市</span>\n  <span>189.81万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                </a>\n            </div>\n            \n        </section>\n        <section class=\"m-list-box\">\n            <h3 class=\"f-cb\">\n                <span class=\"gradient\">完本精选</span>\n                <a href=\"/column/3002.do\" class=\"more\" data-log=\"wa7-0:category=man,eventId=click\">更多</a>\n            </h3>\n            \n          \t\n            <div class=\"m-book-single f-cb\">\n                <a href=/reader/book/ts_a8cd54745ef249098e5f874dd9cf78f8_4  data-log=\"wa7-2:category=man,eventId=click,bookId=ts_a8cd54745ef249098e5f874dd9cf78f8_4\" title=\"超品修仙小农民\">\n                  \n<img src=https://easyreadfs.nosdn.127.net/hn1E9MiCRQXfHGog_OB0Xg==/8796093025071772606 />\n<h3>超品修仙小农民</h3>\n<p>海胆王</p>\n<p>偶然激活神奇玉戒，获上古仙农传承，养的一株金银花竟卖几十万，还一不小心将阿猫阿狗养成上古仙兽……柏小北从此人生逆袭，一路开挂，各色美女更是纷至沓来，桃花朵朵开，人生乐哈哈。</p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span>完结</span>\n  \n  <span>都市</span>\n  <span>478.74万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                </a>\n            </div>\n            \n          \t\n            <div class=\"m-book-single f-cb\">\n                <a href=/reader/book/ts_e3be44e9e384463793f39f199ad55fee_4  data-log=\"wa7-2:category=man,eventId=click,bookId=ts_e3be44e9e384463793f39f199ad55fee_4\" title=\"按摩红人\">\n                  \n<img src=https://easyreadfs.nosdn.127.net/5cLBm501llNC4zHJP5KrsQ==/8796093025397511685 />\n<h3>按摩红人</h3>\n<p>东门小官人</p>\n<p>主动送上门的女人，事后还送上一大笔钱？可素未谋面，还给他介绍美女如云的工作，谁知是福还是祸，先接着再说？</p>\n<p class=\"tag\">\n  \n  <span>完结</span>\n  \n  <span>都市</span>\n  <span>185.29万字</span>\n</p>\n\n                </a>\n            </div>\n            \n        </section>\n        <section class=\"m-list-box rank-box\">\n            <h3 class=\"f-cb\">\n                <span class=\"gradient\">畅销榜</span>\n                <a href=\"/rank/original/list.do?gender=male&type=sell&so